snippet.title: Himawari CATASTROPHE! v1.1.0
snippet.description:
Hack and slash your way through the Garden of the Sun as Tenshi Hinanawi in Himawari CATASTROPHE!

v1.1.0 is out now featuring the new Lunatic difficulty and numerous quality of life changes and fixes!

This game was made in a little over a week for Touhou Fan Game Jam 15, winning 1st place overall!

https://crows-nest.itch.io/himawari-catastrophe
https://itch.io/jam/touhou-jam-15
